The upcoming &#8220;Doctor Dolittle&#8221; movie has been given a release date.&nbsp; The famous animal-loving character is set to return to cinema screens on May 24, 2019, with Robert Downey Jr in the title role, Variety reports. Director Stephen Gaghan has also penned the latest version of the script.&nbsp; In taking on the role of the doctor who can speak to animals, Downey Jr will follow in the footsteps of Eddie Murphy, who last stepped into the character&#8217;s shoes in 2001.-Relax news